data.description:
**OPEN HOUSE 12/30 11-1P** ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 2.99%! Welcome to the thriving community of north Crestview, where convenience meets style. This stunning property is a testament to modern living and thoughtful design.  Situated in a fast-growing locale, the community boasts well-maintained sidewalks and underground utilities.  The Sawyer model itself is a masterpiece, offering a generous 5 bedrooms and 3 baths within its expansive floor plan. The open design seamlessly blends functionality and elegance, providing a fabulous space for both daily living and entertaining.Inside, the home exudes warmth and sophistication with wood-look flooring throughout, complemented by the comfort of carpet in the bedrooms. The open kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a large island bar, a smooth top range, a built-in microwave, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious corner pantry.  Enjoy your meals in a delightful breakfast nook or entertain guests in the separate dining area, adding versatility to your dining experiences.
The master suite is spacious and beautifully appointed, it connects to a luxurious bath offering a double vanity and a generously sized walk-in closet. Step outside to discover a covered patio, perfect for enjoying the outdoors in all weather conditions. Its stylish features and spacious layout make it a best-seller in our community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home in the heart of N. Crestview's growth.
